"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-press-releases-nbc-sports-jac-collinsworth-to-join-peacocks-gold-zone-whip-around-show-during-nbcuniversals-coverage-of-olympic-games-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"STAMFORD, Conn. - July 17, 2024 -NBC Sports'Jac Collinsworthhas been named as a host of theGold Zonewhip-around show, which will stream for the first time live on Peacock during NBCUniversal's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024.Gold Zonewill stream live on Peacock from 7 am - 5 pm ET each day from July 27-Aug. 10.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"score\": 0.9998825057356677, \"rank\": 0.00011750800333038791, \"text\": \"STAMFORD\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9990585765245529, \"rank\": 0.0009422874447834972, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999402082285, \"rank\": 5.96811891431886e-08, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collinsworth, co-host of NBC'sFootball Night in Americafrom on-location each weekand a play-by-play announcer for NBC Sports' college football and basketball coverage, returns for his third NBC Olympics assignment.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7936454350068125, \"rank\": 0.2600054510958654, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, he served as a social media correspondent at the 2016 Rio Games and as an on-location contributor to Peacock'sTokyo Tonightshow at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Collinsworth joins fellowGold ZonehostsScott Hanson,Andrew Siciliano, andMatt Iseman.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 3.910191553852466e-12, \"text\": \"Hanson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Siciliano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 40 events happening simultaneously during the Paris Olympic Games,Gold Zonewill present viewers with the best and most compelling moments happening at any time.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The daily live show will guide fans through the excitement, triumphs, and emotion of the Games, scanning all the events that day to provide viewers with the most exhilarating moments and key races, routines, and finishes as they unfold live.Gold Zone's daily offering will provide viewers with the most comprehensive and all-encompassing live whip-around coverage of any Olympic Games to date.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Collinsworth replacesAkbar Gbajabiamila, who can no longer hostGold Zonedue to a scheduling conflict.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts will often be joined by special guests throughout the day.Gold Zonewill also be available on NBCSports.com and the NBC Sports app via \\\"TV Everywhere\\\" for customers with pay-TV subscriptions.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCSports.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7936454350068125, \"rank\": 0.2600054510958654, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will be the streaming home of the 2024 Paris Olympics, providing fans with the most comprehensive Olympic destination in U.S. media history.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a Summer Games first for Peacock, it will stream every sport and event, including all 329 medal events, and will feature full-event replays; all NBC programming; curated video clips; virtual channels; exclusive original programming; and more.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1953, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9528705022390104, \"rank\": 0.04944687085990742, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more on NBCU's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024, clickhere.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"--PARIS OLYMPIC GAMES--    A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999954586656, \"rank\": 4.540051727464053e-09, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": []}]}"